---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="For Sales Teams — CloakShare" description="Know the moment your prospect reads your proposal. Page-level analytics, real-time alerts, and no per-seat pricing. Track sales document engagement with CloakShare." canonical="/for/sales">
  <section class="pt-32 pb-20 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <p class="font-mono text-accent text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Use Case</p>
      <h1 class="font-mono font-bold text-4xl text-foreground mb-4">For Sales Teams</h1>
      <p class="text-text-secondary font-sans text-lg mb-16 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
        Know the moment your prospect reads your proposal. Page-level analytics show
        which sections they care about, real-time alerts tell you when to follow up, and
        dynamic watermarks prevent unauthorized sharing. No per-seat pricing.
      </p>

      <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2">
        <div class="bg-surface border border-border rounded-lg p-6">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-accent/15 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M3 13.125C3 12.504 3.504 12 4.125 12h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v6.75C7.5 20.496 6.996 21 6.375 21h-2.25A1.125 1.125 0 013 19.875v-6.75zM9.75 8.625c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v11.25c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-2.25a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.125-1.125V8.625zM16.5 4.125c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25C20.496 3 21 3.504 21 4.125v15.75c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-2.25a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.125-1.125V4.125z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-mono font-medium text-foreground mb-2">Page-level analytics</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary font-sans leading-relaxed">
            See which sections your prospect spent the most time on. Know if they read the
            pricing page, skimmed the case studies, or went straight to the contract terms.
            Time follow-ups based on real engagement data.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-surface border border-border rounded-lg p-6">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-accent/15 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M14.857 17.082a23.848 23.848 0 005.454-1.31A8.967 8.967 0 0118 9.75v-.7V9A6 6 0 006 9v.75a8.967 8.967 0 01-2.312 6.022c1.733.64 3.56 1.085 5.455 1.31m5.714 0a24.255 24.255 0 01-5.714 0m5.714 0a3 3 0 11-5.714 0" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-mono font-medium text-foreground mb-2">Real-time engagement alerts</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary font-sans leading-relaxed">
            Get notified the moment a prospect opens your proposal. Webhooks fire instantly
            so your CRM or Slack gets the signal. Follow up while they're still reading,
            not two days later.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-surface border border-border rounded-lg p-6">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-accent/15 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M7.864 4.243A7.5 7.5 0 0119.5 10.5c0 2.92-.556 5.709-1.568 8.268M5.742 6.364A7.465 7.465 0 004.5 10.5a7.464 7.464 0 01-1.15 3.993m1.989 3.559A11.209 11.209 0 008.25 10.5a3.75 3.75 0 117.5 0c0 .527-.021 1.049-.064 1.565M12 10.5a14.94 14.94 0 01-3.6 9.75m6.633-4.596a18.666 18.666 0 01-2.485 5.33" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-mono font-medium text-foreground mb-2">Dynamic watermarks</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary font-sans leading-relaxed">
            Every page of every proposal watermarked with the recipient's email. If a
            prospect shares your pricing with a competitor, you'll know who leaked it.
            Canvas-rendered and non-removable.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-surface border border-border rounded-lg p-6">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-accent/15 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M5.25 5.653c0-.856.917-1.398 1.667-.986l11.54 6.348a1.125 1.125 0 010 1.971l-11.54 6.347a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.667-.985V5.653z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-mono font-medium text-foreground mb-2">Video proposals</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary font-sans leading-relaxed">
            Attach a personalized walkthrough video alongside your proposal. HLS streaming
            with adaptive quality, per-viewer watermarks, and watch-time analytics. No
            other proposal tool does this.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-16 bg-surface border border-accent/30 rounded-lg p-8">
        <h2 class="font-mono font-medium text-accent mb-4">Built for sales teams</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-accent flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
            <span class="text-sm text-text-secondary font-sans">No per-seat pricing — your whole team shares one account, not $65/seat/month</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-accent flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
            <span class="text-sm text-text-secondary font-sans">A 12-person team saves over $9,000/year compared to DocSend</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-accent flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
            <span class="text-sm text-text-secondary font-sans">Password protection for sensitive proposals and contract terms</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-accent flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
            <span class="text-sm text-text-secondary font-sans">Custom domains — send proposals from docs.yourcompany.com</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-accent flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
            <span class="text-sm text-text-secondary font-sans">API and webhooks for CRM integration — pipe engagement data to Salesforce or HubSpot</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 text-center">
        <a href="https://app.cloakshare.dev/register" class="px-6 py-2.5 bg-accent text-background font-mono font-semibold text-sm rounded-md hover:bg-accent-hover transition-colors">
          Try CloakShare free
        </a>
        <p class="text-xs text-text-tertiary font-sans mt-3">Free tier: 50 links, 500 views per month</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
